    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>My Name Is Not Robert</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Sean Bruner letter on Benjamin Weiser's August 6 article views as disturbing New York authorities' response to discovery that Kerry Sanders was wrongfully imprisoned (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>That an overburdened and cynical prison system could make a mistake is understandable, although I would hope that the magnitude of the error in the case of Kerry Sanders is a gross aberration. What is disturbing, also, is that New York authorities responded with denial and defiance rather than with contrition.</p>
        <p>Sean Bruner  Tucson</p>
      </block>
